OL,3,CWoman rescued after petrol bomb attack
OL,4,Con house
OL,6,FA woman has been rescued from a house
OL,7,Fin Saintfield after it was set alight
OL,8,Fin a petrol bomb attack.
OL,10,FPolice said a window was smashed at
OL,11,Fthe house in the Manse Court area
OL,12,Fbefore the petrol bomb was thrown
OL,13,Finside in the early hours of Wednesday.
OL,15,FAn appeal for information has been
OL,16,Fmade about the incident which is being
OL,17,Ftreated as arson with intent to
OL,18,Fendanger life.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
