OL,3,CWoman rescued after petrol bomb attack
OL,4,Con house
OL,6,FThe police said: "At approximately
OL,7,F1.15am, it was reported that a window
OL,8,Fhad been smashed and a petrol bomb had
OL,9,Fbeen throw into the property, causing
OL,10,Fit to catch fire.
OL,12,F"Officers along with colleagues from
OL,13,Fthe Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService attended and a female resident
OL,15,Fwas rescued from house.
