OL,3,CWoman rescued after petrol bomb attack
OL,4,Con house
OL,6,F"This is being treated as arson with
OL,7,Fintent to endanger life and I am
OL,8,Fappealing to anyone who may have
OL,9,Fwitnessed anyone suspicious in the
OL,10,Farea or to anyone with CCTV, doorbell
OL,11,For other footage that could assist
OL,12,Fwith inquiries to contact detectives
OL,13,Fon 101 quoting reference 65 01/04/26."
